snippet.title: Battlefield V – Year 2 Edition Trailer
snippet.description: Welcome to the best way to join Battlefield V. Deploy with the base game’s vast arsenal, plus a catch-up of all weapons and vehicles rewarded across the Chapters of Battlefield V’s first year. Stand out with two Epic soldier outfits and the most popular weapon and vehicle skins from Chapter 1-4 as you fight on iconic battlefields – including the new Pacific theater.
